long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension makes the old school runescape wiki look like an ancient book. It removes a lot of clutter and adds a more relaxing atmostphere to the pages. The extension works only with the new wiki (not the old fandom wiki) and currently looks best on 1920x1080.
